        "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
        "body": "In pandas, `center` just shifts the start/end bounds before performing the rolling aggregation. For reference:\r\n\r\nFor fixed windows e.g. `window=2`\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/pandas-dev/pandas/blob/4e5576d13ab1929aaab9bcc45689939f6d82e178/pandas/core/indexers/objects.py#L105\r\n\r\nFor variable windows e.g. `window=\"2s\"`\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/pandas-dev/pandas/blob/4e5576d13ab1929aaab9bcc45689939f6d82e178/pandas/_libs/window/indexers.pyx#L92",
